  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Explore two of Europe's most famous lakes on your Italian summer getaway.</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to the <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> is a chance to explore two of the most famous lakes in Europe on your summer holiday. Spend a few days getting to know the cobbled streets of <a data-udi="umb://document/d3611d3782e0494ead59e534458bcdd6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3611d3782e0494ead59e534458bcdd6}" title="Bellagio">Bellagio</a>, walking along the Greenway path above <a data-udi="umb://document/164b7f39f6d74033a2991f5799ebdfa7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/164b7f39f6d74033a2991f5799ebdfa7}" title="Lenno">Lenno</a> or eating gelato in <a data-udi="umb://document/80beb49bbb7f416ba46131e7c79367b5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/80beb49bbb7f416ba46131e7c79367b5}" title="Menaggio">Menaggio</a>'s Piazza Garibaldi. Once you've had your taste of Lake Como, head to Lake Maggiore and spend your days hopping between the Borromean islands and admiring botanical gardens whilst based in <a data-udi="umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b}" title="Stresa">Stresa</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/40af41087b6c40cd950bbe672939b005" href="/{localLink:umb://document/40af41087b6c40cd950bbe672939b005}" title="Baveno">Baveno</a>. Why not join some of our Inghams guided walks in Lake Maggiore too?</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,713pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h3>
<ul>
<li>7, 10, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel on Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Return flights or train travel from the UK</li>
<li>Return airport or train station transfers to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Taxi transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
<li>Up to two included guided walks per person per week if staying in Stresa or Baveno</li>
</ul>
