  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Lake Como</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7b6c2ffc51b545748964729d6cf89f5e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b6c2ffc51b545748964729d6cf89f5e}" title="Hotel Bellavista">Hotel Bellavista, Menaggio</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13106288/20240626_170904.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Bellavista, Menaggio" data-udi="umb://media/99368bf6decc4e0ca9eb07390202740d" /></p>
<p>We can't get enough of the views at the Hotel Bellavista - the best ones are from the pool where you can settle down with a good book and gaze out over Lake Como. It's a great base for an active holiday. Being in the centre of Menaggio means there's lots to explore right on the doorstep and you can easily jump on a ferry to get to more lakeside towns.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/13d3ddae817e4c198e3e5f7bea2e415b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13d3ddae817e4c198e3e5f7bea2e415b}" title="Hotel Excelsior Splendide">Hotel Excelsior Splendide, Bellagio</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13091532/ita_bell_exce_01.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Excelsior Splendide, Bellagio" data-udi="umb://media/25803a4396c140838530cd2e5910a38b" /></p>
<p>In a prime position just off Bellagio's lakefront Hotel Excelsior Splendide's good value for money in one of the most popular towns on Lake Como. If you love old-world Italian charm and elegance, then this is the perfect hotel for your Italian summer holiday.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ed3168e942f6443c8c29582c01c0cd4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed3168e942f6443c8c29582c01c0cd4d}" title="Grand Hotel Menaggio">Grand Hotel Menaggio, Menaggio</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13091401/ita_mena_gran_01.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Grand Hotel Menaggio" data-udi="umb://media/b61fab6a5c6e4a05a32d31e839f3db5f" /></p>
<p>Grand Hotel Menaggio has the best location in town. It's right next to the lake and in front of the ferry port so it couldn't be easier to get out for the day to explore Lake Como. It has a real old-world charm - the building is palatial and stands out beautifully on the lakefront.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-como/lenno/hotel-lenno" title="Hotel Lenno">Hotel Lenno, Lenno</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13076237/veranda_mg_5409.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Lenno" data-udi="umb://media/932cea91fc35494b88266880b410c92e" /></p>
<p>Hotel Lenno's right on the lake, so it's easy to find a spot with a nice view and settle down with a good book. It's in the centre of Lenno so it's just a short walk from the local amenities and the ferry port.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Lake Como</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Lake Maggiore</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/fe5b08f98d5c4151878d2ba421369b0c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fe5b08f98d5c4151878d2ba421369b0c}" title="Hotel Royal">Hotel Royal, Stresa</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13077517/_uno7511.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Royal, Stresa" data-udi="umb://media/91fb1dab9bcc40cbb9367cf7e87c6c78" /></p>
<p>Hotel Royal is a lovely, family-run hotel with a relaxed atmosphere. We love the colourful gardens where there's an outdoor pool and plenty of loungers and chairs for you to relax. It's in a nice, quiet location just outside the centre of Stresa. You can walk there in around 20 minutes.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8f2c75297bbc4cfd97537af8e21f423d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8f2c75297bbc4cfd97537af8e21f423d}" title="Hotel Astoria">Hotel Astoria, Stresa</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13077538/hotel-astoria_junior-suite.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Astoria, Stresa" data-udi="umb://media/0c57e950e11d43b1b269bf43a0db5436" /></p>
<p>Hotel Astoria is a family-run hotel on Stresa's promenade. It's very close to the centre so you can easily stroll into town and enjoy the bars, shops and restaurants. The heated pool in the gardens is the perfect place to chill out after a day of walking and sightseeing.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e12eb3765d8e4c08be5209dc6f863ea4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e12eb3765d8e4c08be5209dc6f863ea4}" title="Hotel Milan Au Lac">Hotel Milan au Lac, Stresa</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13100831/adobestock_384607619-2.jpeg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Milan au Lac, Stresa" data-udi="umb://media/3ef6311efa0a47fdbc97c06220e90f07" /></p>
<p>Hotel Milan Au Lac is a firm favourite with Inghams summer guests. It's well located on the promenade and close to the centre of Stresa. There's a nice restaurant with lake views and you can use the pool and gardens at the nearby Hotel Regina Palace.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-maggiore/baveno/hotel-beau-rivage" title="Hotel Beau Rivage">Hotel Beau Rivage, Baveno</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13093785/sala-rossa.jpeg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Beau Rivage, Baveno" data-udi="umb://media/aebd6d44d22b4ea18e798ed76bcbf7a3" /></p>
<p>Hotel Beau Rivage is a fantastic base for walking and for exploring Lake Maggiore. Just a few minutes' walk from the ferry point, you'll never be at a loss for places to visit around the lake.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in Lake Maggiore</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
