  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>Explore two of Italy's most popular lakes on this multi-centre holiday. Start in Lake Como where you can experience some of the most famously photographed towns in the world and then head to Lake Maggiore to explore the lakeside towns and visit t</span><span>he beautiful Borromean Islands.</span></p>]]></listingDescription>
